Package radQC

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutFrame
    The About window displays some information about the application.
    DeviceTypeFrame
    Class for saving XRay device types.
    DisplayInformationFrame
    Class for displaying information about QC tests and dosimetry results for a specific medical unit.
    InterfaceFrame
    BIPM (Bureau International des Poids et Mesures) can perform calibration of exposure (X) for BIPM standard ionization chamber using various X-ray tube settings or various standard gamma sources such 137Cs or 60Co.
    LocationFrame
    Class for saving medical unit location.
    MUFrame
    Class for saving medical unit.
    RadQCFrame
    Main class designed for performing various quality control (QC) tests for XRay equipment used in radiography, mammography, fluoroscopy and CT.
    SearchFrame
    Search for a specific entry in database
